{
  "texts": [
    "However, our language analysis did reveal these significant differences in complexity, and more studies should be conducted on the specific value of these differences.",
    "Finally, our results compared humans to one type of LLM among many others.",
    "It's possible that other LLMs' performance surpasses that of GPT-4 or may not suffer from the same issues that were found in our semantic analysis.",
    "Still, GPT-4 is currently considered state of the art in many different domains, which justifies the comparison of GPT-4 to humans in particular.",
    "Future work"
  ]
}